io.mosip.registration.device.fp

Interface MosipFingerprintProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FingerprintProvider, MantraFingerprintProvider

    public interface MosipFingerprintProvider
    This interface will have the list of FP related functions which needs to implemented in the device specific class. The client class will invoke this interface to communicate with the respective provider based class.
